metadata.name: Ice Study No. 1
metadata.description: Polar opposites.  Frozen and Fluid.  I love this combo.  Pairing these two things together is a goal for this winter.  This image is from December 2018. I was just beginning my journey into monochromatic black and white long exposures.  But even then, I could feel the strength of blending two states together.  Solid and Liquid.
